{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_02_03",
  "title": "井川葵 3話 小言とこんにゃく",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirの合宿後。ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After the LizNoir bootcamp‚ the day of the concert",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2000,
          "startTime": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、そろそろ本番だけど――\nん？　いるのは葵だけか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the big day‚ everyone—\nHold on? Aoi‚ you’re the only one here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "やぁ、みんなは先に行ってもらったよ\nもうスタンバイしてるはずさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey. The others went on ahead.\nThey’re already on standby.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "葵はどうして行かないんだ？　あと10分だぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So what are you still doing here? There are only 10 minutes left.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "こうしてれば、絶対に君が呼びに来てくれるだろう？\nちょっと二人だけで話したくてさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew you’d come to get me‚ if I waited.\nI wanted a word alone with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと愛のことだよな？\nすずは電話しても、何も教えてくれなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is about Rio and Ai again‚ isn’t it?\nI called Suzu but she wouldn’t tell me anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "僕が口止めしたんだ\n本番の楽しみにとっておきたくてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told her not to.\nI wanted to keep it a surprise for the concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "葵は葵で、どうして全然電話に\n出てくれなかったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that why you haven’t been\nanswering my calls either?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……ごめん。合宿中にスマホが壊れちゃったんだ\n連絡出来なくて悪かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s… my bad. My phone got broken at the camp.\nSorry I didn’t try harder to reach out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "責めてる訳じゃない。ただ心配だっただけだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not placing blame. I was just worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "すずが「あの方メッセ送り過ぎですわ」って呆れてたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu was exasperated by you sending too many texts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.93333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　俺、そんなに送ってたかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? I don’t think I sent that many…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "うん。過保護過ぎてお父さんみたいだってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you did. Like an overprotective father‚ she said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、単にすずが好きでメッセしてたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t have a thing for her‚ do you? Is that it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "勘弁してくれよ。マネージャーがアイドルに対して\nそういうことを考える訳ないだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course not. A manager can’t have those feelings\nfor an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "真面目だね、君は。僕はプライベートなら\n誰と付き合ってもいいと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So serious. I think our private lives\nshould be our own. And private.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "莉央は歳が近いし、どうだい？\nなんなら僕は応援してもいいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio is close to you in age. What do you think?\nI’d back you‚ if you want to make a play.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "大人をからかうなって\nそれより、莉央さんと愛はどうなったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re doing it again. Stop mocking your elders.\nAnyway‚ what happened with Rio and Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.66666666666669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "それは今日のライブを観れば分かるよ\n楽しみにしてて。それを伝えたかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll find out when you see the concert.\nSomething to look forward to. That’s all I wanted to say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.433333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、そこまで言うなら……\nじゃあ本番を楽しみにしてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. In that case…\nI look forward to seeing it onstage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、そろそろ時間だ。行ってくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks. It’s time. I’ll catch you afterward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.66666666666669,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.666666666646,
          "startTime": 114.53333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "……次の曲さ、今日のライブでやるって決めて\nみんなで沢山練習したんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…When we picked the next song for today‚\nwe all practiced super hard to get it right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "初めての曲じゃないけど、初めてっていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not the first time‚ but it’s like the first time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.03333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、僕は説明するのは苦手だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I’m no good at explaining this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.96666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "四人になった僕達が、前より成長してるって\n証明してみせるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re going to show you the progress\nthat the four of us have made together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_02_03-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "説明の続きは……\n愛、君にお願いしようかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the rest of the explanation…\nI’m going to turn you over to Ai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2709.5011393229242,
          "startTime": 143.34283447265625
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6466.666666666669,
          "startTime": 147.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
